        <heading>Establishment or enlargement of sewage treatment plant</heading>
        <content>
          <p>  ยง 14-1408 Establishment or enlargement of sewage treatment plant.  The\nboard of trustees of any village may establish a sewage treatment plant\nor enlarge or remodel an existing sewage treatment plant at the expense\nof the village by resolution adopted at a regular meeting. The\nresolution shall state the maximum amount to be expended for such work.\n</p>
